Ha! assassin, what art thou? and he struggled
manfully with the assailant, whereforewhat wouldst
thou?speak!
Thy bloodthy blood! was the only answer, as
the knife was uplifted.
Horrible! but thou wilt fight for it, murderer, was
the reply of Harrison, while, struggling with
prodigious
