paces from each other.
Thou art a Coosaw,exclaimed Harrison,I
know thee.
Chinnabar is the last chief of the Coosaw. He
wants blood for his people.
Thou knowest me, then? said Harrison.
Coosah-moray-te!
was the simple response; and
